		<meta charset="utf-8">
        <meta name="description" content="OpenViva is an free and open source continuation of Project Viva, originally made by Sir Hal. Viva is a VR and non-VR compatible game where you can interact with your very own AI anime character! It is an advanced AI simulation that can interact and respond to many of your actions in a dynamic way through inverse kinematics, complex behaviors, and currently over 200 animations. The character mood is dynamic and responds to how you treat it. You can play with it, feed it, or just be friends with it.">
